Enum Class GenericFolderRequestParameter

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<GenericFolderRequestParameter>
org.odpi.openmetadata.adapters.connectors.governanceactions.watchdog.GenericFolderRequestParameter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<GenericFolderRequestParameter>, Constable
public enum GenericFolderRequestParameter extends Enum<GenericFolderRequestParameter>
MoveCopyFileRequestParameter provides some standard definitions for request parameters used to pass properties to governance actions when they run. Using standard names for request parameters wherever necessary helps to simplify the integration of governance services.
